             was indicted for <rs id="t18300415-7-off37" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300415-7-off37" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300415-7-off37" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
