                  </persName>
            . I am a Police-officer. I heard the prosecutrix call out - I crossed the street, took the prisoner, and found this watch in his trousers pocket; it has been in my possession ever since.(Property produced and sworn to.)[Thursday, April 15.] <rs id="t18300415-7-verdict41" type="verdictDescription">
